---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import LegalPage from "../components/LegalPage.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | LONFRO">
  <LegalPage title="Privacy Policy" intro="How inquiry information and basic website usage data are handled.">
    <h2>Information you provide</h2>
    <p>When you contact us through WhatsApp, email or the inquiry form, we may receive your name, company, contact details, product model, purchase quantity and project requirements.</p>
    <h2>How information is used</h2>
    <p>Information is used to answer inquiries, prepare quotations, evaluate OEM/ODM projects, coordinate samples, support orders and improve customer service.</p>
    <h2>Service providers</h2>
    <p>The initial website may use Formspree or a similar form-delivery provider. WhatsApp and email communications are handled under the policies of their respective providers.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>Google Analytics and TikTok Pixel locations are reserved but inactive until valid IDs are configured. Where required, non-essential analytics will be subject to consent.</p>
    <h2>Retention and requests</h2>
    <p>Inquiry records may be retained for commercial follow-up, order support and legal obligations. You may request access, correction or deletion by emailing liangfen820817@gmail.com.</p>
    <h2>Updates</h2>
    <p>This policy may be updated when the production website, hosting location, form provider or analytics configuration changes.</p>
  </LegalPage>
</BaseLayout>
